section#private.py-5
    .container.py-lg-5
        .row
            .col-12
                h6.top-tile Luxury & Reliability in Every Mile
                h3.title Why Choose Our Premium Services
        .row.g-4.mb-5
            .col-12.col-sm-12.col-md-6.col-lg-4
                .maincard.card.h-100.p-4.transition-hover
                    h4 Premium Private Transfers
                    h5 Start your vacation with first-class comfort
                    p.text-muted.flex-grow-1
                        | Avoid the crowds and the wait. We provide seamless, luxury transportation from Los Cabos International Airport (SJD) directly to your resort or villa. With a modern fleet and professional service, we ensure your arrival is as beautiful as the destination..
            .col-12.col-sm-12.col-md-6.col-lg-4
                .maincard.card.h-100.p-4.transition-hover
                    h4 Professional Local Expertise
                    h5 Navigate the Baja with peace of mind
                    p.text-muted.flex-grow-1
                        | Our bilingual, professional chauffeurs are more than just drivers—they are local experts. Whether you are heading to a world-class golf course or a hidden gem in the Corridor, we guarantee punctual, safe, and stress-free transit every time.
            .col-12.col-sm-12.col-md-6.col-lg-4
                .maincard.card.h-100.p-4.transition-hover
                    h4 Tailored Event Logistics
                    h5 Your itinerary, our priority
                    p.text-muted.flex-grow-1
                        | From high-profile weddings and corporate retreats to private nights out at the Marina, we customize our services to meet your specific needs. Experience a bespoke transportation solution that scales with your group, ensuring everyone travels in style.

style.
    section#private { background-color: #{color7}; }
    section#private h3 {
        color: #{color1};
    }
    section#private h6 {
        color: #{color3};
    }
    section#private .maincard { background-color: #{color5}; }
    section#private h4 { color: #{color3}; margin-bottom: 1rem !important; text-align: center;}
    section#private h5 { align-items: center; color: #{color4}; display: flex; justify-content: center; height: 50px; margin-bottom: 1rem !important; text-align: center;}
    .transition-hover { transition: all 0.3s ease; }
    .transition-hover:hover {
        background: #{color1} !important;
        opacity: 1 !important;
    }
    .transition-hover:hover h4 { color: #{color7} !important; }
